  "detailed_description": "On a daring mission to the stars you and a team of astronauts are dropped at the star system 'Craterous' 100's of lightyears from your home world. You must explore the system and find out what happened to the rest of your fallen team. <br><br>As you explore you can set up mighty outposts and defend them with state of the art Surface to Space Missiles or SSMs.<br>The vastness of space and having to make breathable air is not your only obstacle, alien sentry stations and outposts will be the deciding factor of your survival.<br>Being Stranded will not be all that bad, once the sun sets behind the hills you will be treated to a spectacular view of the night sky, millions of stars and the atmospheres of nearby moons to look at.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras/2c156b69addc13521fb29da25121be1c.avif?t=1675528816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras_big/2c156b69addc13521fb29da25121be1c.avif?t=1675528816 width=800 height=448 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras/c3baba37e54e0d1b8f849e3bc9abc564.avif?t=1675528816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras_big/c3baba37e54e0d1b8f849e3bc9abc564.avif?t=1675528816 width=800 height=344 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras/c350bdcf53a6a9643840f67d06d9286a.avif?t=1675528816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras_big/c350bdcf53a6a9643840f67d06d9286a.avif?t=1675528816 width=800 height=410 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras/fc3f3616db1c11a090004a7e31313ea2.avif?t=1675528816\" width=600 height=272 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras/630a7c1470d6a6ea829cb132b1954726.avif?t=1675528816\" width=600 height=238 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras/11edfac6ace468c2f3e0cd8defe30954.avif?t=1675528816\" width=460 height=215 /></span><br><br>Features :<br>-Every Thing Moves, all planets, all moons<br>-Full Survival<br>-Many building options <br>-Enemies scattered around<br>-Ai bases, you can raid them and use them as a place to build structures of your own<br>-There are more systems than just 'Craterous'<br>-Collisions (Asteroid and Meteor Impacts)<br>*This list will grow as more features are added",
  "about_the_game": "On a daring mission to the stars you and a team of astronauts are dropped at the star system 'Craterous' 100's of lightyears from your home world. You must explore the system and find out what happened to the rest of your fallen team. <br><br>As you explore you can set up mighty outposts and defend them with state of the art Surface to Space Missiles or SSMs.<br>The vastness of space and having to make breathable air is not your only obstacle, alien sentry stations and outposts will be the deciding factor of your survival.<br>Being Stranded will not be all that bad, once the sun sets behind the hills you will be treated to a spectacular view of the night sky, millions of stars and the atmospheres of nearby moons to look at.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras/2c156b69addc13521fb29da25121be1c.avif?t=1675528816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras_big/2c156b69addc13521fb29da25121be1c.avif?t=1675528816 width=800 height=448 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras/c3baba37e54e0d1b8f849e3bc9abc564.avif?t=1675528816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras_big/c3baba37e54e0d1b8f849e3bc9abc564.avif?t=1675528816 width=800 height=344 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras/c350bdcf53a6a9643840f67d06d9286a.avif?t=1675528816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras_big/c350bdcf53a6a9643840f67d06d9286a.avif?t=1675528816 width=800 height=410 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras/fc3f3616db1c11a090004a7e31313ea2.avif?t=1675528816\" width=600 height=272 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras/630a7c1470d6a6ea829cb132b1954726.avif?t=1675528816\" width=600 height=238 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1921610/extras/11edfac6ace468c2f3e0cd8defe30954.avif?t=1675528816\" width=460 height=215 /></span><br><br>Features :<br>-Every Thing Moves, all planets, all moons<br>-Full Survival<br>-Many building options <br>-Enemies scattered around<br>-Ai bases, you can raid them and use them as a place to build structures of your own<br>-There are more systems than just 'Craterous'<br>-Collisions (Asteroid and Meteor Impacts)<br>*This list will grow as more features are added",
